tournaments.about:
The Belarusian Carcassonne Premier League (BCPL) is an online competition for the Carcassonne board game played in real time.

Only Belarusian players are allowed to participate in the tournament.

All games take place on the platform https://boardgamearena.com/

Players compete in a one-on-one round-robin format until two wins (best of 3).

The winners qualify for the offline Championship of Belarus in Carcassonne.
